<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>FMCG & 零售 BI 看板 Skill</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700&family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,400;0,500;1,400;1,500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    :root {
      --text-primary: #111;
      --text-secondary: #64748b;
      --text-muted: #94a3b8;
      --accent: #38bdf8;
      --accent-deep: #0ea5e9;
      --bg: #fafafa;
      --card-bg: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
      --card-border: rgba(14, 14, 12, 0.08);
      --card-shadow: 0 18px 55px rgba(14, 14, 12, 0.06);
      --radius: 20px;
      --radius-sm: 12px;
      --radius-pill: 999px;
      --font-sans: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;
      --font-serif: 'Playfair Display', Georgia, serif;
    }

    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

    body {
      font-family: var(--font-sans);
      background: var(--bg);
      color: var(--text-primary);
      -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
      -moz-osx-font-smoothing: grayscale;
      overflow-x: hidden;
    }

    /* ── Animated Background Blobs ── */
    .bg-blobs {
      position: fixed;
      inset: 0;
      pointer-events: none;
      z-index: 0;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .blob {
      position: absolute;
      border-radius: 50%;
      filter: blur(60px);
      will-change: transform;
    }

    .blob-1 {
      top: -15%;
      right: -8%;
      width: 70%;
      height: 110%;
      background: radial-gradient(ellipse 80% 60% at 70% 40%, rgba(56,189,248,0.35) 0%, rgba(125,211,252,0.2) 40%, transparent 70%);
      animation: flow1 18s ease-in-out infinite;
    }

    .blob-2 {
      top: 15%;
      right: 10%;
      width: 45%;
      height: 55%;
      background: radial-gradient(ellipse 70% 50% at 60% 50%, rgba(34,211,238,0.3) 0%, rgba(103,232,249,0.15) 40%, transparent 70%);
      animation: flow2 22s ease-in-out infinite;
    }

    .blob-3 {
      bottom: -5%;
      left: -5%;
      width: 55%;
      height: 45%;
      background: radial-gradient(ellipse 60% 40% at 50% 80%, rgba(14,165,233,0.25) 0%, rgba(56,189,248,0.12) 40%, transparent 60%);
      animation: flow3 20s ease-in-out infinite;
    }

    @keyframes flow1 {
      0%, 100% { transform: translate(0, 0) rotate(0deg); }
      33% { transform: translate(-30px, 20px) rotate(2deg); }
      66% { transform: translate(20px, -15px) rotate(-1deg); }
    }

    @keyframes flow2 {
      0%, 100% { transform: translate(0, 0) scale(1); }
      50% { transform: translate(-25px, 15px) scale(1.05); }
    }

    @keyframes flow3 {
      0%, 100% { transform: translate(0, 0); }
      50% { transform: translate(20px, -20px); }
    }

    /* ── Navigation ── */
    nav {
      position: fixed;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      right: 0;
      z-index: 50;
      backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
      -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
      background: rgba(250, 250, 250, 0.7);
      border-bottom: 0.5px solid rgba(14, 14, 12, 0.06);
      transition: background 300ms ease;
    }

    .nav-inner {
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 0 32px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      height: 64px;
    }

    .nav-logo {
      font-family: var(--font-serif);
      font-style: italic;
      font-size: 1.35rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: var(--text-primary);
      text-decoration: none;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    }

    .nav-logo span {
      color: var(--accent-deep);
    }

    .nav-links {
      display: flex;
      gap: 36px;
    }

    .nav-links a {
      font-size: 0.875rem;
      color: var(--text-secondary);
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 400;
      transition: color 150ms ease;
    }

    .nav-links a:hover {
      color: var(--text-primary);
    }

    .nav-cta {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 6px;
      padding: 8px 20px;
      font-size: 0.875rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: #fff;
      background: var(--accent-deep);
      border: none;
      border-radius: var(--radius-pill);
      text-decoration: none;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: all 180ms ease;
      box-shadow: 0 1px 8px rgba(14,165,233,0.2);
    }

    .nav-cta:hover {
      opacity: 0.9;
      transform: translateY(-1px);
    }

    /* ── Hero Section ── */
    .hero {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 120px 32px 80px;
    }

    .hero-content {
      max-width: 900px;
      animation: fadeInUp 0.8s ease-out;
    }

    .hero-badge {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      padding: 6px 16px;
      background: rgba(14,165,233,0.08);
      border: 0.5px solid rgba(14,165,233,0.15);
      border-radius: var(--radius-pill);
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: var(--accent-deep);
      margin-bottom: 32px;
      letter-spacing: 0.04em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .hero h1 {
      font-family: var(--font-serif);
      font-weight: 400;
      line-height: 1.1;
      margin-bottom: 28px;
    }

    .hero h1 .line1 {
      display: block;
      font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 4vw, 3.2rem);
      font-style: italic;
      color: var(--text-primary);
    }

    .hero h1 .line2 {
      display: block;
      font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 5.5vw, 4.2rem);
      font-style: italic;
      color: var(--text-primary);
      margin-top: 4px;
    }

    .hero h1 .accent {
      color: var(--accent-deep);
    }

    .hero-sub {
      font-size: clamp(1rem, 1.5vw, 1.2rem);
      font-weight: 300;
      color: var(--text-secondary);
      line-height: 1.6;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto 40px;
    }

    .hero-actions {
      display: flex;
      gap: 14px;
      justify-content: center;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .btn-primary {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      padding: 14px 32px;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: #fff;
      background: var(--accent-deep);
      border: none;
      border-radius: var(--radius-pill);
      text-decoration: none;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: all 180ms ease;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(14,165,233,0.25);
    }

    .btn-primary:hover {
      opacity: 0.92;
      transform: translateY(-1px);
    }

    .btn-secondary {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      padding: 14px 32px;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: var(--text-primary);
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.6);
      border: 0.5px solid rgba(14,14,12,0.1);
      border-radius: var(--radius-pill);
      text-decoration: none;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: all 180ms ease;
      backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
    }

    .btn-secondary:hover {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.9);
      border-color: rgba(14,14,12,0.18);
      transform: translateY(-1px);
    }

    .hero-meta {
      margin-top: 48px;
      font-family: 'SF Mono', 'Fira Code', monospace;
      font-size: 0.7rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.15em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--text-muted);
    }

    @keyframes fadeInUp {
      from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(24px); }
      to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    }

    /* ── Section Common ── */
    section {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
      padding: 100px 32px;
    }

    .section-inner {
      max-width: 1100px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .section-label {
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 0.15em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--accent-deep);
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }

    .section-title {
      font-family: var(--font-serif);
      font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 3.5vw, 2.8rem);
      font-weight: 400;
      font-style: italic;
      line-height: 1.15;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
      color: var(--text-primary);
    }

    .section-desc {
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      font-weight: 300;
      color: var(--text-secondary);
      line-height: 1.6;
      max-width: 640px;
      margin-bottom: 56px;
    }

    /* ── Glass Card ── */
    .glass-card {
      background: var(--card-bg);
      backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
      -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
      border: 0.5px solid var(--card-border);
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      padding: 36px;
      box-shadow: var(--card-shadow);
      transition: transform 300ms ease, box-shadow 300ms ease;
    }

    .glass-card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-3px);
      box-shadow: 0 24px 64px rgba(14, 14, 12, 0.08);
    }

    /* ── Positioning Section ── */
    .positioning-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
      gap: 20px;
    }

    .positioning-card {
      display: flex;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 16px;
    }

    .positioning-icon {
      width: 44px;
      height: 44px;
      border-radius: 14px;
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      flex-shrink: 0;
      font-size: 1.3rem;
    }

    .positioning-card h3 {
      font-size: 1rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: 4px;
    }

    .positioning-card p {
      font-size: 0.875rem;
      color: var(--text-secondary);
      line-height: 1.5;
    }

    /* ── Industry Section ── */
    .industry-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
      gap: 16px;
    }

    .industry-card {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 32px 20px;
      cursor: default;
    }

    .industry-card .icon {
      font-size: 2.2rem;
      margin-bottom: 14px;
      display: block;
    }

    .industry-card h3 {
      font-size: 1rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
    }

    .industry-card p {
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      color: var(--text-secondary);
      line-height: 1.5;
    }

    /* ── Roles Section ── */
    .roles-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(320px, 1fr));
      gap: 16px;
    }

    .role-card {
      display: flex;
      gap: 14px;
      align-items: flex-start;
      padding: 24px 28px;
    }

    .role-emoji {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      flex-shrink: 0;
      width: 40px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .role-card h3 {
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: 3px;
    }

    .role-card p {
      font-size: 0.82rem;
      color: var(--text-secondary);
      line-height: 1.5;
    }

    /* ── Steps Section ── */
    .steps-timeline {
      position: relative;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 0;
    }

    .step-item {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 80px 1fr;
      gap: 0;
      position: relative;
    }

    .step-marker {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .step-num {
      width: 48px;
      height: 48px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent) 0%, var(--accent-deep) 100%);
      color: #fff;
      font-size: 1rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      flex-shrink: 0;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(14,165,233,0.25);
      position: relative;
      z-index: 2;
    }

    .step-line {
      width: 2px;
      flex: 1;
      background: linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(14,165,233,0.3), rgba(14,165,233,0.08));
      margin: 4px 0;
    }

    .step-content {
      padding: 8px 0 48px 0;
    }

    .step-content h3 {
      font-family: var(--font-serif);
      font-size: 1.4rem;
      font-weight: 400;
      font-style: italic;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
    }

    .step-content .step-goal {
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      color: var(--accent-deep);
      font-weight: 500;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }

    .step-content p {
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      color: var(--text-secondary);
      line-height: 1.6;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }

    .step-content ul {
      list-style: none;
      padding: 0;
    }

    .step-content ul li {
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      color: var(--text-secondary);
      padding: 4px 0;
      padding-left: 18px;
      position: relative;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }

    .step-content ul li::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      left: 0;
      top: 11px;
      width: 6px;
      height: 6px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: var(--accent);
    }

    /* ── Components Table ── */
    .table-wrapper {
      overflow-x: auto;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }

    .components-table {
      width: 100%;
      border-collapse: separate;
      border-spacing: 0;
      font-size: 0.88rem;
    }

    .components-table thead th {
      text-align: left;
      padding: 14px 20px;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 0.78rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.06em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--text-secondary);
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(14,14,12,0.08);
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.4);
    }

    .components-table thead th:first-child {
      border-radius: var(--radius-sm) 0 0 0;
    }

    .components-table thead th:last-child {
      border-radius: 0 var(--radius-sm) 0 0;
    }

    .components-table tbody td {
      padding: 13px 20px;
      border-bottom: 0.5px solid rgba(14,14,12,0.05);
      color: var(--text-secondary);
    }

    .components-table tbody tr:hover td {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
    }

    .components-table tbody td:first-child {
      font-weight: 500;
      color: var(--text-primary);
    }

    /* ── Deliverables Section ── */
    .deliverables-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
      gap: 20px;
    }

    .deliverable-card {
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .deliverable-card::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      right: 0;
      height: 3px;
      border-radius: var(--radius) var(--radius) 0 0;
    }

    .deliverable-card:nth-child(1)::before {
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--accent), var(--accent-deep));
    }

    .deliverable-card:nth-child(2)::before {
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, #6366f1, #8b5cf6);
    }

    .deliverable-card:nth-child(3)::before {
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, #10b981, #059669);
    }

    .deliverable-card .d-icon {
      font-size: 1.8rem;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }

    .deliverable-card h3 {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .deliverable-card p {
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      color: var(--text-secondary);
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    /* ── Notes Section ── */
    .notes-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
      gap: 16px;
    }

    .note-card {
      padding: 28px;
    }

    .note-card .note-num {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      width: 28px;
      height: 28px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: rgba(14,165,233,0.1);
      color: var(--accent-deep);
      font-size: 0.78rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 14px;
    }

    .note-card h4 {
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
    }

    .note-card p {
      font-size: 0.82rem;
      color: var(--text-secondary);
      line-height: 1.55;
    }

    /* ── Footer ── */
    footer {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 60px 32px 48px;
      border-top: 0.5px solid rgba(14,14,12,0.06);
    }

    footer p {
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      color: var(--text-muted);
    }

    footer .footer-logo {
      font-family: var(--font-serif);
      font-style: italic;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      color: var(--text-primary);
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    /* ── Responsive ── */
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .nav-links { display: none; }

      .hero { padding: 100px 24px 60px; }

      section { padding: 64px 20px; }

      .step-item { grid-template-columns: 56px 1fr; }

      .step-num { width: 40px; height: 40px; font-size: 0.85rem; }

      .positioning-grid,
      .roles-grid,
      .deliverables-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }

      .industry-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
    }

    /* ── Scroll Animations ── */
    .animate-in {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(20px);
      transition: opacity 0.6s ease, transform 0.6s ease;
    }

    .animate-in.visible {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <!-- Background Blobs -->
  <div class="bg-blobs">
    <div class="blob blob-1"></div>
    <div class="blob blob-2"></div>
    <div class="blob blob-3"></div>
  </div>

  <!-- Navigation -->
  <nav>
    <div class="nav-inner">
      <a href="#" class="nav-logo">BI<span>Skill</span></a>
      <div class="nav-links">
        <a href="#positioning">定位</a>
        <a href="#industries">行业</a>
        <a href="#roles">角色</a>
        <a href="#workflow">流程</a>
        <a href="#components">组件</a>
        <a href="#deliverables">交付物</a>
      </div>
      <a href="#workflow" class="nav-cta">
        <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M13 2L3 14h9l-1 8 10-12h-9l1-8z"/></svg>
        开始使用
      </a>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-content">
      <div class="hero-badge">FMCG & 零售行业</div>
      <h1>
        <span class="line1">标准化</span>
        <span class="line2">BI 看板 <span class="accent">Skill</span></span>
      </h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">
        帮助数据分析师为快消品及零售行业制作标准化 BI 看板，覆盖零食量贩、饮料、乳制品、商超、便利店、社区零售六大行业。
      </p>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a href="#workflow" class="btn-primary">
          <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
          五步工作流
        </a>
        <a href="#deliverables" class="btn-secondary">
          <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M14 2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v16a2 2 0 002 2h12a2 2 0 002-2V8z"/><polyline points="14 2 14 8 20 8"/><line x1="16" y1="13" x2="8" y2="13"/><line x1="16" y1="17" x2="8" y2="17"/><polyline points="10 9 9 9 8 9"/></svg>
          查看交付物
        </a>
      </div>
      <p class="hero-meta">Quick BI · Markdown · 标准化流程</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Positioning -->
  <section id="positioning">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="animate-in">
        <p class="section-label">Skill 定位</p>
        <h2 class="section-title">三大标准化交付物</h2>
        <p class="section-desc">本 Skill 为快消品及零售行业提供完整的 BI 看板解决方案，从需求诊断到最终交付，全流程覆盖。</p>
      </div>
      <div class="positioning-grid animate-in">
        <div class="glass-card positioning-card">
          <div class="positioning-icon" style="background:rgba(14,165,233,0.08);">📄</div>
          <div>
            <h3>PRD 文档</h3>
            <p>完整的产品需求文档，明确看板的业务目标、使用场景、数据来源和功能需求。</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="glass-card positioning-card">
          <div class="positioning-icon" style="background:rgba(99,102,241,0.08);">📊</div>
          <div>
            <h3>看板设计稿</h3>
            <p>基于 Quick BI 组件的可视化设计方案，包含页面布局、图表类型和联动逻辑。</p>
